[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 7124,
        "end_time": 11153,
        "text": "Professor Fukan\u014d, the famous \neccentric scientist and adventurer,"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 11153,
        "end_time": 13254,
        "text": "has embarked on a new challenge:"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 13254,
        "end_time": 17894,
        "text": "flying around the world nonstop\nin a plane of his own design."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 17894,
        "end_time": 22434,
        "text": "Able to travel consistently at the\nincredible speed of one degree longitude"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 22434,
        "end_time": 24645,
        "text": "around the equator per minute,"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 24645,
        "end_time": 28725,
        "text": "the plane would take six hours\nto circle the world."
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 28725,
        "end_time": 30243,
        "text": "There&#39;s just one problem:"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 30243,
        "end_time": 34335,
        "text": "the plane can only hold 180 kiloliters\nof fuel,"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 34335,
        "end_time": 37576,
        "text": "only enough for exactly half the journey."
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 37576,
        "end_time": 38465,
        "text": "Let&#39;s be honest."
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 38465,
        "end_time": 41816,
        "text": "The professor probably could have\ndesigned the plane to hold more fuel,"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 41816,
        "end_time": 43695,
        "text": "but where&#39;s the fun in that?"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 43695,
        "end_time": 47605,
        "text": "Instead, he&#39;s devised a slightly more\nelaborate solution:"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 47605,
        "end_time": 51575,
        "text": "building three identical planes\nfor the mission."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 51575,
        "end_time": 53056,
        "text": "In addition to their speed,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 53056,
        "end_time": 56525,
        "text": "the professor&#39;s equipped them\nwith a few other incredible features."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 56525,
        "end_time": 59046,
        "text": "Each of the planes can turn on a dime"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 59046,
        "end_time": 64026,
        "text": "and instantly transfer any amount\nof its fuel to any of the others in midair"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 64026,
        "end_time": 65415,
        "text": "without slowing down,"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 65415,
        "end_time": 67795,
        "text": "provided they&#39;re next to each other."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 67795,
        "end_time": 69876,
        "text": "The professor will pilot the first plane,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 69876,
        "end_time": 74686,
        "text": "while his two assistants Fug\u014dri\nand Orokana will pilot each of the others."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 74686,
        "end_time": 78237,
        "text": "However, only one airport,\nlocated on the equator,"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 78237,
        "end_time": 80787,
        "text": "has granted permission for the experiment,"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 80787,
        "end_time": 82316,
        "text": "making it the starting point,"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 82316,
        "end_time": 83456,
        "text": "the finish line,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 83456,
        "end_time": 85736,
        "text": "and the only spot where \nthe planes can land,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 85736,
        "end_time": 86855,
        "text": "takeoff,"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 86855,
        "end_time": 88816,
        "text": "or refuel on the ground."
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 88816,
        "end_time": 90717,
        "text": "How should the three planes coordinate"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 90717,
        "end_time": 95487,
        "text": "so the professor can fly continuously\nfor the whole trip and achieve his dream"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 95487,
        "end_time": 98576,
        "text": "without anyone running out \nof fuel and crashing?"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 98576,
        "end_time": 102246,
        "text": "Pause here if you want \nto figure it out for yourself."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 102246,
        "end_time": 103656,
        "text": "Answer in: 3"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 103656,
        "end_time": 104656,
        "text": "Answer in: 2"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 104656,
        "end_time": 106118,
        "text": "Answer in: 1"
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 106118,
        "end_time": 108187,
        "text": "According to the professor&#39;s calculations,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 108187,
        "end_time": 111398,
        "text": "they should be able to pull it off\nby a hair."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 111398,
        "end_time": 115457,
        "text": "The key is to maximize the support\neach assistant provides,"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 115457,
        "end_time": 118677,
        "text": "not wasting a single kiloliter of fuel."
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 118677,
        "end_time": 121007,
        "text": "It also helps us to think symmetrically"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 121007,
        "end_time": 123810,
        "text": "so they can make shorter trips\nin either direction"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 123810,
        "end_time": 128267,
        "text": "while setting the professor up for a long\nunsupported stretch in the middle."
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 128267,
        "end_time": 129838,
        "text": "Here&#39;s his solution."
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 129838,
        "end_time": 133117,
        "text": "All three planes take off at noon\nflying west,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 133117,
        "end_time": 136488,
        "text": "each fully loaded with 180 kiloliters."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 136488,
        "end_time": 139850,
        "text": "After 45 minutes, or one-eighth\nof the way around,"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 139850,
        "end_time": 143314,
        "text": "each plane has 135 kiloliters left."
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 143314,
        "end_time": 147828,
        "text": "Orokana gives 45 to the professor\nand 45 to Fug\u014dri,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 147828,
        "end_time": 149989,
        "text": "fully refueling them both."
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 149989,
        "end_time": 153441,
        "text": "With her remaining 45, \nOrokana returns to the airport"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 153441,
        "end_time": 156778,
        "text": "and heads to the lounge\nfor a well-deserved break."
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 156778,
        "end_time": 159958,
        "text": "45 minutes later, with one-quarter\nof the trip complete,"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 159958,
        "end_time": 165009,
        "text": "the professor and Fug\u014dri\nare both at 135 kiloliters again."
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 165009,
        "end_time": 168548,
        "text": "Fug\u014dri transfers 45 \ninto the professor&#39;s tank,"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 168548,
        "end_time": 172148,
        "text": "leaving himself with the 90\nhe needs to return."
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 172148,
        "end_time": 175478,
        "text": "Professor Fukan\u014d stretches\nand puts on his favorite album."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 175478,
        "end_time": 177309,
        "text": "He&#39;ll be alone for a while."
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 177309,
        "end_time": 181459,
        "text": "In the meantime, Orokana has been\nanxiously awaiting Fug\u014dri&#39;s return,"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 181459,
        "end_time": 185009,
        "text": "her plane fully refueled and ready to go."
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 185009,
        "end_time": 190659,
        "text": "As soon as his plane touches the ground,\nshe takes off, this time flying east."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 190659,
        "end_time": 194059,
        "text": "At this point, exactly 180 minutes \nhave passed"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 194059,
        "end_time": 197260,
        "text": "and the professor is at the halfway point\nof his journey"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 197260,
        "end_time": 200069,
        "text": "with 90 kiloliters of fuel left."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 200069,
        "end_time": 201579,
        "text": "For the next 90 minutes,"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 201579,
        "end_time": 204749,
        "text": "the professor and Orokana&#39;s planes \nfly towards each other,"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 204749,
        "end_time": 207511,
        "text": "meeting at the three-quarter mark."
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 207511,
        "end_time": 209990,
        "text": "Just as the professor&#39;s fuel \nis about the run out,"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 209990,
        "end_time": 212110,
        "text": "he sees Orokana&#39;s plane."
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 212110,
        "end_time": 215291,
        "text": "She gives him 45 kiloliters \nof her remaining 90,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 215291,
        "end_time": 217970,
        "text": "leaving them with 45 each."
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 217970,
        "end_time": 221049,
        "text": "But that&#39;s just half of what they need\nto make it to the airport."
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 221049,
        "end_time": 226680,
        "text": "Fortunately, this is exactly when Fug\u014dri,\nhaving refueled, takes off."
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 226680,
        "end_time": 231280,
        "text": "45 minutes later, just as the other two\nplanes are about to run empty,"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 231280,
        "end_time": 234240,
        "text": "he meets them at the 315 degree point"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 234240,
        "end_time": 239920,
        "text": "and transfers 45 kiloliters of fuel\nto each, leaving 45 for himself."
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 239920,
        "end_time": 244620,
        "text": "All three planes land at the airport\njust as their fuel gauges reach zero."
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 244620,
        "end_time": 247010,
        "text": "As the reporters and photographers cheer,"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 247010,
        "end_time": 251541,
        "text": "the professor promises his planes will\nsoon be available for commercial flights,"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 251541,
        "end_time": 254750,
        "text": "just as soon as they figure out how \nto keep their inflight meals"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 254750,
        "end_time": 256611,
        "text": "from spilling everywhere."
    }
]